Wadsworth Harris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wadsworth_Harris 0 Wadsworth Harris (October 9, 1864 – November 1, 1942) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 46 films between 1911 and 1936. He was born in Boston, Massachusetts and died in Los Angeles, California from pneumonia.
